      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <img src="/images/budget.jpeg" alt="Budget Management"
             onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/150?text=ðŸ’°'">
        <h3>Budget Management</h3>
        <p>Track family expenses, set spending limits, and manage shared finances. Get insights into your spending patterns and save more effectively.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <img src="/images/events.jpeg" alt="Activity & Event Planning"
             onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/150?text=ðŸ“…'">
        <h3>Activity & Event Planning</h3>
        <p>Plan family activities, schedule events, and coordinate gatherings. Keep everyone in sync with shared calendars and event reminders.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
